  /*
  ---INFO---
  snippet to block mega xovers
  y'all know those works that have every fandom on the archive?
  y'all know what i'm talking about i know you do
  i found this... somewhere. idk i don't remember
  this lets you block them
  change nth-of-type(n) to a number 1 larger than the maximum you want
  so say you'll allow 4 fandoms
  change (n) to (5)
  */
.blurb:has(h5.fandoms):has(a.tag:nth-of-type(n)) {
  display: none !important;
}
